The article announces several nominations and appointments made by the President. Some of the notable nominations include Susan Parker Bodine as Assistant Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency, Dan R. Brouillette as Deputy Secretary of Energy, James Donovan as Deputy Secretary of the Treasury, Kevin Allen Hassett as Chairman of the Council of Economic Advisers, and Derek Kan as Under Secretary of Transportation for Policy. There are also nominations for various other positions such as Ambassador to The Bahamas, Commissioner of the Commodity Futures Trading Commission, Member of the Occupational Safety and Health Review Commission, and Assistant Secretary of Veterans Affairs.